        "title": "docs: restore OpenClaw-hosted ClawHub docs",
        "body": "## Summary\n- Reverts the ClawHub docs migration commits that moved docs hosting/linking toward ClawHub-owned routes and domains.\n- Restores ClawHub app, package, email, and inspector docs links to `https://docs.openclaw.ai/clawhub`.\n- Removes the app-hosted docs builder/proxy/subdomain wiring while preserving unrelated validation-test improvements and the `/auth/docs` callback endpoint used by the OpenClaw docs assistant.\n\n## Reverted\n- `fix: serve docs subdomain root (#2630)`\n- `feat: move docs to canonical subdomain`\n- `docs: serve ClawHub docs with shared OpenClaw renderer (#2609)`\n\n## Compatibility Kept\n- `/auth/docs` remains mounted outside the docs route tree so OpenClaw-hosted docs can post Ask Molty auth through ClawHub without making ClawHub host docs pages.\n\n## Validation\n- `bunx vitest run playwright.config.test.ts convex/lib/emails.test.ts emails/emailTemplates.test.tsx convex/packageInspectorNode.test.ts convex/packages.public.test.ts src/__tests__/header.test.tsx src/__tests__/ui-design-contract.test.ts src/__tests__/skills-publish-route.test.tsx src/__tests__/plugins-publish-route.test.tsx src/__tests__/package-detail-route.test.tsx src/lib/docsAuth.test.ts src/routes/auth/-docs.test.tsx src/components/AppProviders.test.tsx` - 13 files passed, 334 tests passed.\n- `bun run --cwd packages/clawhub test:src -- src/cli/commands/packages.test.ts` - 1 file passed, 66 tests passed.\n- `bunx tsc --noEmit --pretty false` - passed.\n- `bun run ci:static` - passed.\n- `git diff --check` - passed.\n- `rg -n \"https://clawhub\\\\.ai/docs|https://docs\\\\.clawhub\\\\.ai|docs\\\\.clawhub\\\\.ai|clawhub\\\\.ai/docs|DOCS_SITE_CANONICAL_ORIGIN|openclaw-docs-site|scripts/docs-builder|docs:smoke|docs:build\" . --glob '!node_modules/**' --glob '!bun.lock'` - no matches.\n",
